Package com.razer.sdk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Callback
    Callback class for Razer Auth SDK
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CallbackManager
    The CallbackManager manages the callbacks and consumes data from onActivityResult() method
    LoginManager
    Singleton class for initiating the auth flow.
    Token
    This class represents an immutable Token for using Razer APIs
    UserAPI
    Api for accessing user Razer information
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TokenExpiredException
    Exception thrown when the access token passed to the login manager is no longer valid.
    UserNotLoggedException
    Thrown when the sdk does not have a valid Token.
